----------------------------------------------------------------------
  Full equation: M*(k) = (D4(k)/D2(k)) * 0.74829 * 0.1167
  C(k) = C_0 * [1 + alpha*(M*(k) - M*_0)]  with alpha=38.3, C_0=29.17pF

